  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located near Gallipoli and nestled in the heart of a rich and verdant pine grove overlooking the Ionian sea, this recently renovated four-star property offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere with stellar levels of service. With its elegant Mediterranean décor and proximity to three spectacular beaches within a two mile radius, Costa Brada is home to 76 stylish rooms with a modern and minimalist feel, featuring beach white washed furniture with most offering sea views.</p>
<p>There are three restaurants including the Panoramic Restaurant for fine dining, Fico d'India for poolside Mediterranean cuisine and Solebrado known for its grilled meat, fish and brick-oven pizzas. Breakfast is served in the elegant dining room with a vast and rich continental selection on offer to help start your day. A bright and generously sized pool is located within the hotel gardens, overlooking the azure seas below and adjacent to restaurant Fico d'India which is perfect for the days when you just want to kick back and bask in the <a data-udi="umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd}" title="Puglia &amp; Basilicata">Puglian</a> sunshine. The Grand Hotel Costa Brada is also home to three private beaches stretching across 380 metres of golden sandy shores. All three beaches offer waiter service, lifeguards, mini club for children (3 hours per day, selected dates) and sun loungers and parasols which are free of use for hotel guests from 01 Jun - 30 Sep 20. </p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Grand Hotel Costa Brada is approx. 1 hour 5 mins from Brindisi Airport</p>]]></description>
