  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Comfort Side Sea View Rooms </strong>are approximately 19m² and sleeps two people. They are bright, spacious and airy with air conditioning, minibar, safe, 22" LCD TV with SKY, wifi, slippers and en suite bathroom with shower. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are 30m² and sleep two to four people. They are styled beautifully with hues of Mediterranean golds and whites and offer exceptional views out towards the cyan waters of the Ionian sea. </p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>are 49m² and can sleep up to four. They are incredibly spacious with a relaxed and quiet atmosphere and views out over the Baia Verde. Located on the first floor, these fabulous rooms are home to a king sized bed and en suite bathroom with bath and shower. A large balcony offers panoramic sea views.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
